column2: Over the last 2 weeks, how often have you been bothered by any of the following problems?
column11: If you checked off any problems, how difficult have these problems made it for you to do your work, take care of things at home, or get along with other people?

column2: Feeling nervous, anxious, or on edge
column3: Not being able to stop or control worrying
column4: Worrying too much about different things
column6: Being so restless that it is hard to sit still
column8: Feeling afraid as if something awful might happen
